1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:02,876
Here is one useful thing to watch for.

2
00:00:02,826 --> 00:00:06,940
Copy does not remove the text; it leaves it where it is.

3
00:00:06,940 --> 00:00:09,062
Only Cut takes it away.

4
00:00:09,062 --> 00:00:13,722
If it happens, pause, reset, and try again calmly.

